| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1329 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d3d19c2-f66a-55b3-acb9-a9beac3388e3"
